[[File:Prosenjit.jpg|thumb|upright|150px|[[Jeet (actor)|Jeet]] (top), [[Dev (actor)|Dev]] (middle) and [[Prosenjit Chatterjee]] (bottom) are top three highest paid Bengali actors]]

Salaries for the highest Bengali paid film actors currently range from {{INRConvert|30|l}} to {{INRConvert|40|l}}, but an actor can earn substantially more by deferring all or part of their salary against a percentage of the film's gross, known within the industry as a "profit participation" deal. Since not all salaries are made public. The figures are given at their [[Real versus nominal value (economics)|nominal value]], since earnings from profit based deals are accumulated over many years, making it unfeasible to adjust for [[inflation]].

